{"type": "article", "id": 24377, "title": "咖啡过滤器", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-24T07:00:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163808NnSgwZH2VCyfsxiR.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个咖啡过滤器，它一共有三层，每一层盒子都是一道过滤网，你需要将磨碎后咖啡豆倒入最上面一层盒子里，然后摇动整个盒子使碎末分层，就可以筛选出细末状的和石头块（boulders）的，其中细末状是口感最好的，而那些像石头块一样凝固的只能增加苦味。过滤器的过滤层是可替换的，产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/rafino/the-rafino-coffee-grind-refining-system?token=070c7081\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163803UArKlWs51k0bg9dV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163803UYwnFvCRt2mzN0lf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163804XOrf7kZv6HqwpuaP.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163805IUlAcvuYLM826WCR.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021638071yj0zVdw9AcLPXfk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}